M+Shift	Switch language
w+Enter	Open with
f2	rename selected file
ctrl+shift+esc	open task manager
alt+f4	close
ctrl+f4	close tab
win+e	open explorer
win+r	open run
win+up	maximize current window
win+down	shrink current window ( or minimize )
shift+mouseright+(copy as path)
Alt+PrintScreen	snapshot of the current Window only
win+m	minimize all
win+l	lock computer
ctrl+backspace	delete whole word